Akwukwu-Igbo, bụ isi ụlọ ọrụ nke Oshimili North Local Government Area nke Delta State nke Nigeria
Ọ dị na mpaghara Delta North nke steeti ahụ
Ọrụ ndị obodo ahụ na-abụkarị ọrụ ugbo na ịkụ azụ

O nwere ọtụtụ akụkụ nke gụnyere Ogbe -Ani, Ogbe-Onihe, Umu Onai, Ogbe Obi, Ogbe Iyase, Umuekeke, Achala, Umu-Olum, Umu- Opu wdg.
A na-akpọ ala a "Ala nke Ndị Agha Ọzara" mgbe ụfọdụ

Otu oge Attorney General nke Federal Republic of Nigeria (Late Chief Michael Ashikodi Agbamuche) na May Agbamuche-Mbu INEC National Commissioner- Chair of Legal Services and Supervising Bayelsa, Edo and Rivers States.
